    "And we construct our local point force dataset in two parts: for the first part, we use a physics simulator to generate videos of a ball rolling across the ground; and for the second part, we use a model (Zhang et al., 2024a) which integrates 3D Gaussians and a physics simulator to generate videos of a plant being poked.",
